title: Anoushka Shankar - Full Performance (Live on KEXP)
description:
http://KEXP.ORG presents Anoushka Shankar performing live in the KEXP studio. Recorded October 17th, 2023.

Songs:
Boat To Nowhere
Secret Heart
Dancing In Madness
Stolen Moments 

Anoushka Shankar - Sitar
Tom Farmer - Bass
Arun Ghosh - Clarinet
Pirashanna Thevarajah - Percussion
Sarathy Korwar - Drums

Host: Jyoti Patel
Audio Engineers: Kevin Suggs, Julian Martlew, James Campbell
Mastering: Matt Ogaz
Cameras: Jim Beckmann, Carlos Cruz, Alaia D’Alessandro, Scott Holpainen, Ettie Wahl
Editor: Jim Beckmann
